lead_paragraph: Manchester United manager Jose Mourinho has no concerns over striker Zlatan Ibrahimovic's barren spell as he expects the Swede's "brilliant" attitude to soon be rewarded with goals.

headline.print_headline: Mourinho Lauds Zlatan's Attitude Despite Lack of Goals
headline.main: Mourinho Lauds Zlatan's Attitude Despite Lack of Goals
